==Value==
I would like to start a discussion about the value we create and what we offer to lure people in for membership.


* social aspect-cross pollination
* actual quiet space (coffee shop, Dennys) to work--do you get a desk?, or just a locker? 24 hours?
* tools (hardware and software)
* presenters/classes (apple model)
* Most importantly, Something you don't know you wanted or were missing!
